com.ihealth.communication.control

Class Po3Control

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ihealth.communication.control.Po3Control
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DeviceControl, UpDeviceControl

    public class Po3Control
extends java.lang.Object
implements DeviceControl, UpDeviceControl
    Public API for the PO3

    The class provides methods to control PO3 device. You need to call the device method, and then call the connection method

    If you want to connect a PO3 device, you need to call iHealthDevicesManager.startDiscovery(int) to discovery a new PO3 device, and then call iHealthDevicesManager.connectDevice(java.lang.String, java.lang.String)to connect PO3 device.
